    Feature 0118: Enhanced Rescan + Script Reordering
    
    Phase 1: Enhanced Rescan
    - Added scene detection to rescanScript (detects new scenes)
    - Added position updates for existing scenes via updateScenePositions
    - Fixed locationTypes parameter in bulkImportLocations
    - Updated EditorToolbar toast to show scene counts
    
    Phase 2: Script Reordering
    - Created reorderScriptContent helper function
    - Integrated script reordering into moveScene
    - Script text now updates immediately when scenes are moved on beat board
    - Editor marked as dirty for 60-second auto-save
    
    Phase 3: Hybrid Scene Matching
    - Created matchScene helper (ID first, heading+position fallback)
    - Integrated hybrid matching into rescanScript and updateScenePositions
    - Robust matching handles edge cases (duplicate headings, missing IDs)
    
    All changes are frontend-only, no backend changes required.

